{"tid":698591,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"出得嚟行預左要還","createTime":"2018-06-11T23:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T23:57:50.000Z","uid":118999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"efdf7e609b6521075de3b96ed7aeac0e010c3fe4","tid":698591,"uid":118999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T23:37:57.000Z","msg":"發現開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出嚟搞政治，對抗呢個中共痴線政權就應該預左比人秋後算帳，6年係多，但家下執政黨係中共，如無意外之後幾十年都係。<br />\n老實講大把人比中共搞死過，又軟禁又被自殺，起碼你6年後出嚟又一條好漢，滿滿的光環，全香港都記得你個名。<br />\n但係前排跟你地去衝擊政府，集會遊行要入獄果班後生仔呢？無人記得無人提，出到嚟只係一個有案底又無工作經驗既人。公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0521277d1d64a6e7b1a09fce2b6ed994c21fc7","tid":698591,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T23:57:50.000Z","msg":"6年？可能6日後已經冇人提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}